songs.title: Oh Me Oh My (Demo)
songs.lyrics:
[Chorus]
Oh me (Yah), oh me, oh my (Yah, yah)
I done lost some ones and I can't even lie
Oh me (Yah), oh me, oh my (Yah, yah)
I just shut the club down, I didn't even try (Yah)
Oh me, oh me, oh my
Yah, yah, yah, yah
Oh me, oh me, oh my
I just shut the club down, I didn't even try

[Verse]
Pulled from the club around 3:30
I've been up in it, go James Worthy
I've been up, goin' up, way up
Thinkin' about it all day, fuck
How many more could fit in the ride?
Hit me, I'll pull up on any side
All of my niggas on M
All of my bitches off M
Open, open up, baby
You know that I'm goin', goin', goin', goin' right now
Hundred bottles, we get poppin' right now
Smokin', don't you choke on dopest right now
Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah
Oh me, oh my, homie, don't try
Won't you come home for a ride?
We can do this for the night

[Bridge]
Yah, my, my, my
How time fly, fly
On the up and up, yeah
In it, I'm in it, I got it, [?]

[Chorus]
Oh me, oh me, oh my
Yah, yah, yah, yah
Oh me, oh me, oh my
I just shut the club down, I didn't even try
